So we look at the aggregate
prepayment.

00:25:29.730 --> 00:25:31.220
That's the old fashioned way.
 

00:25:31.220 --> 00:25:34.763
And we say, "What
percentage of the remaining

00:25:34.763 --> 00:25:36.788
