00:25:36.788 --> 00:25:38.538
So you'd make a function like
this.

00:25:38.538 --> 00:25:41.576
You'd say, "Well,
prepaid might equal 10

00:25:41.576 --> 00:25:42.680
percent."
 

00:25:42.680 --> 00:25:44.828
Why am I picking 10 percent?
 

00:25:44.828 --> 00:25:51.734
So if you go back to this
picture you see that prepayments

00:25:51.734 --> 00:25:58.519
