when nothing's happening.

00:25:58.519 --> 00:26:03.273
So you say 10 percent plus
maybe you're going to get some

00:26:03.273 --> 00:26:08.451
more prepayments so you might
write--well, I just wrote down a

00:26:08.451 --> 00:26:10.660
function plus the min.
 

00:26:10.660 --> 00:26:13.252
The min, say,
of .60 because it never seems

00:26:13.252 --> 00:26:16.834
