00:26:43.130 --> 00:26:47.769
So what does this say?
 

00:26:47.769 --> 00:26:48.740
What happens?
 

00:26:48.740 --> 00:26:51.784
You're normally going to
pay--so this is this whole

00:26:51.784 --> 00:26:55.239
function here,
so I should write this as .1

00:26:55.239 --> 00:26:58.349
plus, can you see that over
