00:27:41.798 --> 00:27:46.402
I just multiply it by some
constant, but it'll never go up

00:27:46.402 --> 00:27:48.259
more than 60 percent.
 

00:27:48.259 --> 00:27:49.538
That's what this function says.
 

00:27:49.538 --> 00:27:53.134
And sigma, this is the
volatility--all right,

00:27:53.134 --> 00:27:55.828
