00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:06.450
It never gets above 60 percent,
but as the incentive to prepay,

00:28:06.450 --> 00:28:08.150
as interest rates get lower and
the incentive to prepay

00:28:08.150 --> 00:28:10.230
