00:33:25.118 --> 00:33:27.996
Of course we hired them anyway,
but they'd always get this

00:33:27.996 --> 00:33:28.400
wrong.
 

00:33:28.400 --> 00:33:32.012
So the question is,
suppose you've got a group of

00:33:32.012 --> 00:33:36.230
people like this and you figure
out what the value of the

00:33:36.230 --> 00:33:38.883
mortgage is,
and interest rates have been

00:33:38.883 --> 00:33:40.058
