00:33:40.058 --> 00:33:43.648
Let's suppose for one month
interest rates shoot down,

00:33:43.648 --> 00:33:46.425
interest rates collapse and
half the pool,

00:33:46.425 --> 00:33:49.000
60 percent of the pool
disappears.

00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:51.780
So now you've only got 40
percent of the people left you

00:33:51.780 --> 00:33:54.713
had before, and then interest
rates return to exactly where

00:33:54.713 --> 00:33:56.130
