00:34:40.284 --> 00:34:41.733
they're not
&gt;

00:34:41.733 --> 00:34:43.503
option properly and
&gt;

00:34:43.503 --> 00:34:44.469
their mortgages?
 

00:34:44.469 --> 00:34:45.340
Prof: Exactly.
 

00:34:45.340 --> 00:34:47.900
So that's an incredibly
important point.

00:34:47.900 --> 00:34:49.900
It's called the opposite of
adverse selection.

00:34:49.900 --> 00:34:55.233
Every one of these events is
selecting the people left not

00:34:55.233 --> 00:34:57.563
